### ============================================================
### 个人衣柜 - 搭配管理接口测试
### 服务器地址: http://localhost:8080
### ============================================================

### ============================================================
### 前置条件：先创建衣物测试数据
### ============================================================

### 1. 创建衣物测试数据（如果尚未创建）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/clothing/test-data

### 2. 获取所有衣物列表（获取衣物 ID 用于搭配测试）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/clothing

### ============================================================
### 搭配 CRUD
### ============================================================

### 3. 创建搭配（完整搭配：外套 + 上衣 + 裤子 + 鞋子）
### 请将 outer/top/bottom/shoes 替换为实际衣物 ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outfit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "春日出游风",
  "items": {
    "outer": "outer-clothing-id",
    "top": "top-clothing-id",
    "bottom": "bottom-clothing-id",
    "shoes": "shoes-clothing-id"
  },
  "card_image": ""
}

### 4. 创建搭配（最小搭配：仅上衣 + 裤子）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outfit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "简约日常风",
  "items": {
    "top": "top-clothing-id",
    "bottom": "bottom-clothing-id"
  },
  "card_image": ""
}

### 5. 创建搭配（含裙子 + 配饰）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outfit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "优雅裙装风",
  "items": {
    "top": "top-clothing-id",
    "skirt": "skirt-clothing-id",
    "shoes": "shoes-clothing-id",
    "accessory": "accessory-clothing-id"
  },
  "card_image": ""
}

### 6. 获取所有搭配
GET http://localhost:8080/api/outfit

### 7. 获取搭配摘要列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/outfit/summary

### 8. 获取搭配详情（替换 :id 为实际搭配 ID）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/outfit/outfit-id-here

### 9. 复制搭配（替换 :id 为实际搭配 ID）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outfit/outfit-id-to-clone/clone
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "复制的春日出游风（微调版）"
}

### 10. 删除搭配（替换 :id 为实际搭配 ID）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/outfit/outfit-id-to-delete

### ============================================================
### 测试数据
### ============================================================

### 11. 创建搭配测试数据（3 套默认搭配）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outfit/test-data

### ============================================================
### 错误场景测试
### ============================================================

### 12. 创建搭配 - 缺少必选项（没有上衣）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outfit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "缺少上衣",
  "items": {
    "bottom": "some-bottom-id"
  },
  "card_image": ""
}

### 13. 创建搭配 - 裤子和裙子同时选择（互斥）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/outfit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "冲突测试",
  "items": {
    "top": "some-top-id",
    "bottom": "some-bottom-id",
    "skirt": "some-skirt-id"
  },
  "card_image": ""
}

### 14. 获取不存在的搭配详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/outfit/non-existent-id

### 15. 删除不存在的搭配
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/outfit/non-existent-id

### ============================================================
### 注意:
### - 运行测试前请先确保服务器已启动
### - 先运行 #1 创建衣物测试数据，然后用 #2 获取衣物 ID
### - 将获取到的 ID 填入 #3-#5 的 items 字段中
### - 使用 VS Code REST Client 插件或 IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client 运行
### ============================================================
